creator: Krish Compusoft Services Pvt Ltd
descriptionHtml:
• You can Analyze, Store, Share, Download health documents, reports and images in single App.
• Single comprehensive easily accessible medical history which allows health professionals to more accurately diagnose, monitor and treat medical conditions.
• Book an appointment with your doctor and doctor can manage appointment.
• Doctor can add Health details (Health problems, Medical condition, medication and allergy), order lab test, add vitals and body indices details of their patient.
• You can add family member in their personal health record and check all your family member’s health records at a time.
• Print, share your emergency medical card and carry with you always as it allow to add contacts in emergency from your phone book. Make this emergency card as your lifesaver.
• Manage your Body indices, Vitals for healthy lifestyle.
• The intuitive charts, helpful tips, Medicine Reminder, Appointment Reminder & insurance reminder and Vaccination reminder in one place.
• Achieve your fitness and diet goals. You can also personalize your Health Calculator by adding or removing Goals.
• Receive daily tips, Alert and reminders if any.
Discover how H-Connect can be your lifesaver by creating a fully connected health system with your personalized integrated health information.
• Download H-Connect today and connect with your health care provider/beloved ones at anytime from anywhere.
